title: The MGM Cyberattack Is Worse Than I Thought...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at a cyberattack happening on the MGM group of casinos in Las Vegas for a few days at this point. With most services down and the staff rolling back to the days of pen and paper, a lot of info has come out and a good portion of it is misleading. What's the truth? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
